import * as React from 'react';
import { Button } from 'react-native-web';
import { Header,
        Container,
        Title,
        HeaderButtonLeft,
        HeaderButtonRight,
        Container1,
        Container2,
        Container3,
        Container4,
        Text1,
        Text2,
        Text3,
        Text4,
        Title1,
        Button1,
        Container5,
        Circulo,
        Text5,
        Text6,
        Text7
    } 
from './styles';
import { View,StyleSheet,Text} from 'react-native';
import { Entypo } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';



function AddAlarmScreen({navigation,route}) {
    const item = route.params;
    return(
        <Container>
            <Header>
                <HeaderButtonLeft>
                    <Ionicons name="chevron-back" size={20} color={"black"} onPress={navigation.goBack} />
                </HeaderButtonLeft>
                <HeaderButtonRight>
                    <Entypo name="dots-two-horizontal" size={20} color="black" />
                </HeaderButtonRight>
                <Title>Add Alarm</Title>
            </Header>
            <Container1>
                <Ionicons name="bed-outline" size={30} color="#7B6F72" /> 
                <Text1>Bedtime</Text1>
            </Container1>
            <Container2>
                <Text2>Hours of sleep</Text2>
            </Container2>
            <Container3>
                <Text3>Repeat</Text3>
            </Container3>
            <Container4>
                <Container5></Container5>
                <Circulo></Circulo>
                <Text4>vibrate When Alarm Sound</Text4>
            </Container4>              
            <Button1 onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Tela 6')}>               
                <Title1>Add</Title1>
            </Button1>
            <Text5>09:00 PM</Text5>
            <Text6>8hours 30minutes</Text6>
            <Text7></Text7>
            <Button
                title="Go to"
                onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Tela 6')}
            />
        </Container>
        
    );
};


export default AddAlarmScreen;
